snippet.title: Lethal League Blaze Teaser
snippet.description:
Join the Reptile Hideout for the latest information: https://discord.gg/ekTTtJr

Coming soon: https://store.steampowered.com/app/553310/Lethal_League_Blaze/

Lethal League Blaze is coming to PC and console in 2018.

http://lethalleagueblaze.com/

Animator
Niels Schaap

Sound Effects

Voice of Candyman
Carlos Ramirez

Voice of Doombox
Oscar van der Burgh

yotube

Music:
Klaus Veen - Ordinary Days V2
Excerpt from B.Bravo & Lean Rock - Shred
